===Noun===
'''auto de fé'''

# Refers to the ritual of public [[penance]] of condemned heretics and apostates that took place when the Spanish [[inquisition|Inquisition]] or the Portuguese Inquisition had decided their punishment (that is, after the trial). The phrase also commonly occurs in English in its Portuguese form ''auto da fé''.

